OL,4,Csentencing hearings to get more jail
OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FNew powers for judges to punish
OL,8,Fcriminals who refuse to attend their
OL,9,Fsentencing hearings sends a "clear
OL,10,Fmessage" that offenders cannot "opt
OL,11,Fout" of justice, victims' families
OL,12,Fhave said.
OL,14,FPlans for tougher sanctions in England
OL,15,Fand Wales, including more jail time or
OL,16,Floss of privileges in prison, are
OL,17,Famong the measures in the Government's
OL,18,FVictims and Courts Bill to be
OL,19,Fintroduced to Parliament on Wednesday.
