OL,7,FThe move comes after a series of high
OL,8,Fprofile offenders refusing to face
OL,9,Fvictims' families sparked a public
OL,10,Foutcry, and calls by campaigners for a
OL,11,Fchange in the law.
OL,13,FFamilies of murdered primary school
OL,14,Fteacher Sabina Nessa, law graduate
OL,15,FZara Aleena and mother-of-three Jan
OL,16,FMustafa are among those to have
OL,17,Fcampaigned for the change after their
OL,18,Floved ones' killers were absent from
OL,19,Fsentencing hearings.
