OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FReacting to the "long-awaited"
OL,8,Fproposals, Ms Nessa's sister Jebina
OL,9,FIslam, Ms Aleena's aunt Farah Naz and
OL,10,FMs Mustafa's cousin Ayse Hussein,
OL,11,Fsaid: "This move holds offenders to
OL,12,Faccount.
OL,14,F"It sends a clear and necessary
OL,15,Fmessage: the justice system is not
OL,16,Fsomething you should be able to opt
OL,17,Fout of.
