OL,7,F"It is not about punishment through
OL,8,Fforce ` but about ensuring that
OL,9,Fperpetrators cannot remove themselves
OL,10,Ffrom the consequences of their
OL,11,Factions."
OL,13,FTheir joint statement said the
OL,14,Flegislation was a "step in the right
OL,15,Fdirection" alongside wider campaigns,
OL,16,Fand that the proposed punishments
OL,17,Findicated "this change is being taken
OL,18,Fseriously".
