OL,7,FCheryl Korbel and her family have
OL,8,Fcampaigned to change the law so that
OL,9,Foffenders are compelled to appear in
OL,10,Fthe dock for sentencing.
OL,12,FThomas Cashman, the gunman who killed
OL,13,FOlivia as he chased a drug dealer who
OL,14,Fhad tried to run into her home in
OL,15,FKnotty Ash, Liverpool, did not appear
OL,16,Fin court to hear his life sentence in
OL,17,FApril 2023.
