OL,7,FMs Korbel's MP, Anneliese Midgley,
OL,8,Fsaid of the legislation: "This law is
OL,9,Fdown in no small part to my
OL,10,Fconstituent Cheryl Korbel. I am so
OL,11,Fproud of her.
OL,13,F"Sentencing is not just a legal
OL,14,Fformality; it is the culmination of
OL,15,Fjustice. That's why it's so important
OL,16,Fthat justice is not only done, but
OL,17,Fseen to be done.
OL,19,F"Olivia's Law will make sure it is."
