OL,7,FEarlier this year, triple crossbow and
OL,8,Fknife killer Kyle Clifford refused to
OL,9,Fattend his sentencing where he
OL,10,Freceived a whole life order in March,
OL,11,Fwhile Southport child-murderer Axel
OL,12,FRudakubana avoided facing victims'
OL,13,Ffamilies as he was removed from his
OL,14,Fhearing for repeatedly shouting in
OL,15,FJanuary.
OL,17,FThe measure could apply to any case in
OL,18,Fthe crown court, and include those
OL,19,Fsuch as Rudakubana who attended
OL,20,Fproceedings but was removed from the
OL,21,Fcourtroom for disruptive behaviour.
