OL,7,FVictims' Commissioner for England and
OL,8,FWales, Baroness Newlove, said: "These
OL,9,Fimportant and welcome reforms give the
OL,10,FVictims' Commissioner the statutory
OL,11,Fpowers needed to deliver on the role's
OL,12,Fpromise: championing victims' rights,
OL,13,Fscrutinising compliance with the
OL,14,FVictims' Code, holding agencies to
OL,15,Faccount, and spotlighting the true
OL,16,Fvictim experience to drive meaningful
OL,17,Fchange.
